# Ads Operations Production Rule

Ads are allowed only if they do not damage learning trust.

Required:
- placements
- campaigns
- providers
- frequency caps
- safety rules
- performance metrics
- audit log
- privacy controls
- RBAC-aware admin actions

Forbidden:
- ads during flashcard review
- ads during timed BJT/quiz questions
- popup ads over learning content
- ads disguised as learning buttons
- sending raw learning history to ad providers
- fake revenue metrics
- placeholder-only admin page